Paccayapaccanīyānuloma
Nahetuduka
81.
2243Nahetupaccayā ārammaṇe satta, anantare satta, samanantare satta, sahajāte dvādasa, aññamaññe nava, nissaye dvādasa, upanissaye satta, purejāte satta, āsevane cattāri, kamme dvādasa, vipāke nava, āhāre dvādasa, indriye dvādasa, jhāne dvādasa, magge tīṇi, sampayutte satta, vippayutte dvādasa, atthiyā dvādasa, natthiyā satta, vigate satta, avigate dvādasa.
